Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Old Year
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.35,0:01:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all my matches were over for the year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became bedridden with a terrible fever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I curled up in my dimly-lit room,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and December 31st,\Nthe last day of the year, arrived.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.21,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... thirsty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Water...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something... Have to eat something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and take some medicine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have just one pill left...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Need to go buy... But I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too bothersome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or rather, impossible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well. I'll just go back to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll fall asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.34,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll go to sleep and maybe when I wake up,\Nmy fever will be down like it never happened.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I stayed in the apartment for days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Delirious with fever,\NI had the same dream over and over again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.04,0:03:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one I've had repeatedly,\Never since I was a kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream where I'm going up\Na long, long escalator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not scary or anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just go up and up\Nand when I reach the top...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there's no way back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who's there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So noisy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't. I can't get up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}M-Momo. What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rei-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it, I knew you had a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Okay, charge!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! Rei's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina, secure the pillow!\N- Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Uh, Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Fluff
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, get your phone, wallet, and keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can stay in your pajamas,\Nbut put a coat on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.30,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, wrap this scarf around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.84,0:05:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a taxi waiting downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A taxi? Why? Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gleam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the doctor, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if you have the flu,\Nyou'll be quarantined and taken care of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we'll bring you to our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Comfy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:26.32,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fluff\NFluff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing it wasn't the flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to be careful, with an elderly person\Nand a toddler in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's egg porridge. Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your kitchen.\NYou haven't been eating for a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.01,0:05:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with pickled plums?\NI'm going to mix it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's refreshing when you have\Na bad taste in your mouth from a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Rei. Stretch out your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This towel goes around your neck,\Nand we'll change it when you sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eating porridge makes you sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.02,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to sweat a lot\Nto make your fever go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've got plenty of towels,\Nso we'll change them again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.03,0:06:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just wiping the sweat off your forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even fluffier than before,\Nnow full fluffy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo wants to thank the meal too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, this is for Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you ate quite a bit. Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some tea\Nand then you can go lie down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Internal Medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...let's call your home in Mejiro.\NThey're probably worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm living on my own now.\NSo I think it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Tangerines, huh?\N- I'm not a fan of citrus...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tangerines, tangerines...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On your own, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see your phone, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your phone's been dead\Nfor about three days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Charging
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}Call Log\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKawamoto Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call\NKouda Dad Missed Call
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't say "I'm on my own" when\Nyou have people worried about you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. It's Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei? It's really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You weren't picking up your phone,\Nso I was about to go over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure you're okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment I heard\Nmy father's voice on the phone,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.47,0:07:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realized how thoughtless I had been.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:08:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From his voice, I could tell\Nthat he was really worried about me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My thoughts kept spinning around in my head,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.69,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but in the end,\NI had just been thinking about myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get up? Let's eat something\Nand take some medicine again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me when Aiko's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me when Sayuri Ishikawa is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please wake me up...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when it's time to eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Zzzzz
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We had three more people then,\Nso it was pretty packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Snore Snore
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, it's like we were\Nrunning out of oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Three people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, we looked\Nat those sleeping faces and complained,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while Mom, Grandma, and I\Nwould be cleaning things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we saw the old year go,\Nand the new year come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There must be a reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody in this house talks about their father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's eat, Rei. You must be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were sleeping soundly,\Nso I didn't wake you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's mix some pickled plums in there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be refreshing even if you can't\Ndistinguish flavors because of your fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I said that earlier, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom always said that to me when I had a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying the same thing, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I heard those words,\NI would think, "She's saying it again,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it was really comforting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They were like magic words.\NMom's magic words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.89,0:10:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she was gone before Momo\Nhad the chance to hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.15,0:10:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On an important day like New Year's Eve,\Neven though I'm not part of your family,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you brought me here and took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong. I wanted you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you weren't here,\Nright now I would probably be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cleaning up by myself and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Kiriyama. Why are you the one crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As we were sniffling\Nand frantically searching for tissues,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we heard the New Year's Eve bells\Nringing from the TV.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so this year came to a pathetic end,\Nvanishing into the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had been distracted by my own loneliness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that I failed to recognize\Nsomeone else's loneliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To my foolish self, the New Year's bells\Nfell upon me gently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a wide, flowing river,\Nthe New Year was slowly on its way in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.03,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Old Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:39.03,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who put stickers on my drawers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I'm sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sheesh!\NIt's really difficult to peel this off, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, can you get up?\NSis says it's time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's your fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's gone down a lot.\NI should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.33,0:12:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning. Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many ads in the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:37.59,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Momo! I'm reading the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama, want some mochi?\NWhat topping?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet soy sauce for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese for Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll have cheese, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's continue on. Go ahead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:12:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's still a little bit hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's eat first.\NAnd then take some medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, get in the kotatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pajamas leave your feet cold, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:14.96,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hot\NHot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:14.96,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twitch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the mailman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! New Year's postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:20.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wheee
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one's for me, for Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me, for me, for Sis, for Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Here's one for Momo, too.\N- Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hm Hm, What, What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did we get a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Maybe we'll get\Na New Year's gift-postcard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, postcards came for Momo, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.53,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From nursery school\Nand the pediatrician
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Maybe you got postcards\Nat your place, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huff\NHuff
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't think there would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get them for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hang tight, I'll be right back!\N- Wait, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I'm borrowing your key!\N- I feel like you'll just stand out a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}20 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm back...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Can't look him\Nin the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Y-You got New Year's postcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got postcards?\NI thought there wouldn't be any.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Happy New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Bodoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of cottage is that? A palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A hot air balloon? Pasted with CG?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kiriyama!! I'm looking forward\Nto the day we can battle each other in C1!!\N- Nikaidou
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it's really flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ba-Baam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japan Shogi Association
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chairman of the Japan Shogi Association,\NTakanori Jinguuji, 16th Grandmaster,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman... Um... What about shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sailfish? Malaysia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Who is that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Looks like he did it.\N- A fisherman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say this. He was a strong player.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Although he's always been a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still, he served\Nas a master for seven seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I defending him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.85,0:14:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year! It's me, Aunt Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:02.65,CenterSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going to my husband's parents' house\Nmakes my shoulders stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Aunt Misaki, look at Momo's\NNew Year's postcards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're pretending.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Have some tea, Aunty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been preoccupied\Nwith outward appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, thank you, Hina.\NYou're very thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you're good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's money.\NHere you are, Hina and Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! What should I buy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me too? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Akari, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you sure, Aunty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. For you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Shogi Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I hear Akari kidnapped you\Nafter you got sick on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even me? But I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It was a while ago,\Nbut you brought Issa and Smith to my bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.29,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heh-heh\Nheh-heh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Glare
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Mom. Mikako. Misaki's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.86,0:16:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of me this year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Misaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Akari going to work there again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop using your relatives\Nand get a new girl in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put Akari in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dad. My bar is not a dangerous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's small, but it's refined and mainly caters\Nto regular customers. It's my treasured palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to keep Akari at home, doing all\Nthe housework and childcare until she gets old?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.06,0:17:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a serious girl, so she'll just commit herself\Nto becoming a mother figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twice a week, even if forced to,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she should put on makeup,\Nwear a pretty outfit, and go outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a beautiful girl, so what will you do\Nif she becomes weary
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from house chores\Nand misses her chance to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone lay a finger\Non Akari at the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.34,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, rather, I'll simply take their money\Nwithout letting them touch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... It's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because they can't touch her,\Nthey'll get worked up
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and men's habits of spending money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll grab it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.60,DefaultLef2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black pearl\Nfrom the\NSouth Seas
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Your daughter is a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave birth to a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aunty, what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you stay to eat\NHina's and my labor of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. Then, sure, I'll have dinner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, your uncle went to see\Na soccer game anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ta-daaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are diligent!\NYou made traditional New Year's food?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in a modern style! It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina and I planned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We thought about it\Nand packed it with auspicious food items.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But aimed to make traditional\NNew Year's food that's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we bought red and white fish cake,\Nwe wouldn't finish it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so instead we used red and white pounded\Nfish cake balls, and put them on skewers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pork and beans, so we can all live hearty lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.03,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Golden mashed, sweetened chestnuts\Nto increase luck with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lotus root burdock,\Nso we can see through things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Burdock root meat rolls, to stay firmly rooted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mini hamburger turtles\Nto pray that Grandpa has a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Long life
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, rolled omelette\Nmixed with fish paste, sweet egg strips...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I tried cutting little hot dogs\Ninto the shape of a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:02.85,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Person who mainly ate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:02.85,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proud
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mikako and your grandmother would always\Nmake the traditional New Year's food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Put in spaghetti, too.\NAnd gum. Gum, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Meowmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}New Year's food... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They express wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at this nest of boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it kind of makes me feel like\NI have to fill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And when we do fill it, the sense\Nof achievement is absolutely wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was like, "Mission accomplished!"\NLike, "Wow!" It felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.50,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yahooey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly, it's extremely important\Nto cultivate that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from a "sense of achievement"\Nin your everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that. I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. "Sense of achievement"\Nand "pain in the neck" go hand in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you get the "sense of achievement"\Nby overcoming that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come again.\NLet's have another great year together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's this late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.25,0:20:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Hina, would you give Momo a bath?\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wash the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Kiriyama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to use this space,\Nso would you go upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use this space?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.47,0:20:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is the first time you've seen it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the Kawamoto bath is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.61,0:20:40.74,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open the living room door\Nand suddenly a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.82,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.11,0:20:40.74,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And no changing room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before, we didn't have a tub,\Nso we went to a public bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the family got bigger, so they made\Nthis bathroom addition to the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're all girls, and I'd like to add\Na changing room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if we did that, it would take up\Nmore yard space and cost money.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's troublesome when a guest comes over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.89,DefaultLeftM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Change of Clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.89,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bath towel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G-Goodnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.90,0:21:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What an unusual house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.12,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I took the medicine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This string is convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's kind of strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can I sleep like it's normal at the house\Nof a family I've only known for a little bit?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do I feel so at peace when I'm here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did I have a dream about those days?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This old house...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}had time, everyone, everything, even me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.52,0:22:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all gently embraced together,\Nand then dozed away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I fell asleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the kind of deep, peaceful sleep\Nthat I hadn't had in such a long time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:23:00.04,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:35.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get it, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.81,0:24:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How much money am I saving\Nfrom the food budget?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.60,0:24:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Momo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.40,0:24:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a match that I really need to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.74,0:24:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so busy!\NI can even borrow some cat paws!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.74,0:24:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.74,0:24:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'll do it instead. Please watch\Nthe next episode of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Busy, busy, busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.28,0:24:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"March Comes in Like a Lion" meow.
